				<td colspan="2"><span>alright, this is kinda of a rant post but here we go.
<br />

<br />
First off i'd like to start with GoD, i think this expansion is the first off to lead in the downfall of EQ, although i do not have this expansion (therefore cant comment on any of the zone content or anything) but GoD seems to have just popped out of nowwhere, its somewhere on norrath (island?) also some of the loot of the upper tier zones is sickaning, i mean u pretty much already got epic 2.0's out there, go look in ugua or txiciutsn or sghbdfiugbd (were they on crack when they made those names?), ok now on to OoW, i admit being lvl 70 would be pretty cool but just think about what bards and druids and other soloing classes will be able to do, epic 1.0's will take a total of 2 hours, unless u have to camp something, in PoP 2 ppl will take out LMM (on E`ci someone did it with 11) ppl will be able to farm anything, and quarm will be like farming HQ bear pelts (although on some servers this already happens) i just think OoW will complete the downfall of EQ.
<br />

<br />
sorry if i sound like a noob or whatever, go ahead flame away =P
<br />

<br />
what are ur guys's opinons about the upcoming expansion?</span></td>
